Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  你干什么去了  这么晚才回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经为这事情道过歉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能轻饶  今天说好五点前回家的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做为男人应当遵守诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp53}　{\fsp1}Cream Stew{\r}\N好不容易做的奶油杂烩都凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它热一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的烦死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为大丈夫是不会向妹妹的攻击屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这把刀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿夏树这家伙没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树还真有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是佩服的时候  我正心烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也吃完饭再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我得早点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树那家伙太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在今天来这儿之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去千秋家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室扫除谁来干？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来后自然会做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天正巧想早点洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话  让我过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为大丈夫要在极近的距离躲过妹妹的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿他没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底接不接受妹妹的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  夏树君曾这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近觉得冬马举止越来越像假小子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系  冬马变得男性化的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也会用对待男生的态度对待她的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  冬马变得像女生一点他就不会生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  找什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这张这么女生的照片作为证据给夏树看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次午睡后照的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回可不像假小子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快生气的时候就给他看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿这照片给他看没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆不惹他生气不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑去干什么了  不成体统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土豆炖肉都已经不成样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它热一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说好会早点回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:11:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈真有你的  没生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过几天就是冬马生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没正经送过什么礼物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说的  我可有过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（哥哥  LOVE）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必冬马那时很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那玩意儿的反作用才使得冬马变成这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送的才合她心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（恋爱诊断  GAME）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要送那种玩意给不久前还上幼稚园的小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许现在还用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会派上用场的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天？我…我坚决不认可这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙最喜欢我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为经常陪冬马玩游戏  所以我非常了解她的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那游戏机都已经被你玩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马当时大失所望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么送什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:12:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了解下头儿的最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头儿嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一代是我们家的春香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代是阿优
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四代是藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么二代是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该上高一了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汇报二代头儿事迹之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一让学校第一的小混混南夏树束手无策的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  头儿风范十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  南夏树是你家亲戚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是亲戚哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是遗憾  没有什么特别的情报了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二代头儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树那眼神的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘带钱包了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  好难为情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我客气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我吃章鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少吃一顿没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然忘带钱包了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说夏树  你想的事全写在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没被那样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么试着打我一拳  绝对打不到我哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打中了  午餐算我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为男人欠钱必还
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我才说的那么巧妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为男人决不打女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:18.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希你少来  这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不那绝对是真的  那时候我可称的上是天才呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  真希吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树这眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像对着自己所憧憬的年长女性那样深情地望着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你向我要求成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你用那种眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可以的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是仁美吗  怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  失…失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是你把她弄哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示自己被误解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:12.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弾む鼓動とジャンプしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:12.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}情绪激动地跳了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}軽やかなスピードで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这轻快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日だって突き抜けちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛能穿越明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:23.89,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心変わりもご愛嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:23.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}改变心意也有可爱之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せのアンテナは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸福的天线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一つじゃ足りないです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}岂能只有唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:36.12,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}七色ツバサ広げて　願いを届けに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:36.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开七色翅膀  去传达愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:43.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔の磁石　ハートにぎゅっと　急がなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:43.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欢笑的磁铁  揪紧内心  必须加快速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.11,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうだっ！ハチャメチャ元気に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}没错！  用不可思议的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.95,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ハッピー集めちゃいましょ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.95,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来收集幸福！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:56.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真面目じめじめ悩んでないで　カラッと笑い飛ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:56.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要认真地在那烦恼纠结  爽朗地一笑而过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:02.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ぐっと↑ポジティブシンキング　絶対カラフル宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:02.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}GOOD↑积极思考  绝对绚丽多彩的宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:06.40,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}志を打ち上げろ　GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:06.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}表露志向  GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:11.37,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来ロケット駆けてく　追いつけ追い越せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:11.37,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冲向未来的火箭  追上去赶超吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  社团方面的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…怎么样才能变得成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你不问春香而来问我真是找对人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  想必真希学姐也在努力想变得成熟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不爽  这事还是去找成熟的春香问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保…保坂学长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香确实向着成熟迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为她处于必须要接受别人的撒娇的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她内心深处肯定渴望着能向谁撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…保坂学长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么拿着伞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么全身湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在二年级的教室前面游荡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问的好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天突然下起了雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我又没带伞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挚爱的人  带伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一忘带的话  我就默不作声地把伞递给她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不由自主冒着大雨把家里最好的伞拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛把扣子解开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了随时能奉上雨伞  我就等在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热气…还有潮气…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你们所见  我的举手投足都是有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  水溅过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的成熟就是奉上雨伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树那眼神  肯定是忘记带伞正伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘带伞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给你  给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的太丢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有把塑料伞  别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此不如借我那把塑料伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿去  给
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色…兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树这眼神…犹如散发着希望的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救啦  放晴了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香莫非你忘记带伞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  妹妹们忘带了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是妹妹们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马给  这是生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  夏树没生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  多亏了春香呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  没什么哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  南家三姐妹～欢迎回来～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是极密情报
